<h2>Mailing List</h2>

<p>
There is an official support mailing list for WML users:
</p>

<div class="box">
<b>wml-users</b> <b>@</b> <b>thewml.org</b>
</div>

<p>
Here you can reach the WML maintainer Denis Barbier and the
other people who use WML and which can help you in case of
problems. Use this forum to spread your ideas and suggestion,
too. Feel free to ask anything WML-related you want.
This mailing-list is international and all messages must be
posted in English.
</p>

