<h2>Subscription</h2>

<p>
To subscribe to this Majordomo-controlled mailing list, just send an E-mail to
<tt>petidomo</tt><tt>@thewml.org</tt> with only
</p>

<div class="indent">
<p>
<tt>subscribe wml-users</tt> <i>you@domain.dom</i>
</p>
</div>

<p>
in the <i>body</i> (leave the subject empty). After sending this, Majordomo
will respond with an authority challenge which has to send back again for
security reasons (to avoid that others subscribe you without your ok). Now you
are successfully subscribed to this list.
</p>

<p>
Please notice that this list allows only subscribers to post because of the
existing spamming services. So make sure you're already subscribed before
posting and that your E-mail address when posting is the same as used when you
subscribed. If it's not possible for you to use exactly this address please
mail <a href="mailto:rse@engelschall.com">Ralf S. Engelschall</a> the
additional addresses you want to allow posting.
</p>
